{"tid":2014823,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東方日報立場近年變左好多","createTime":"2020-05-13T09:07:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-15T06:36:13.000Z","uid":128261,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3869b4930e2044454d033496d83efe1065b0ebe0","tid":2014823,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:07:51.000Z","msg":"不妨睇下面兩篇評論<br />\n以前東方日報仲夠膽批評中共<br />\n而家變左同文匯大公無分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140922/00184_002.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20140922%2F00184_002.html&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=cfdb825e\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20140922/00184_002.html</a><br />\n<br />\n共產黨自稱三個代表，只是自我感覺良好而已，如今的共產黨與以前的共產黨已不可同日而語，他們既代表不了人民，更代表不了國家，人民莫名其妙「被代表」，還要莫名其妙「被愛黨」，這才是最大的笑話。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130801/00184_005.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20130801%2F00184_005.html&d=RJ6DAKdT%2BAkj0rfdhPz9NYlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=f2006e9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20130801/00184_005.html</a><br />\n<br />\n在這樣的「強勢」宣傳、強詞奪理下，北京鼓吹的「愛國愛港」在許多港人心中就成了「愛黨」的同義詞，成了「愛黨」的政治邏輯，成了「愛國愛港」就是要「聽黨話，跟黨走」。"},{"pid":"10b13571d4d16070272069b895d9152a9b187ae8","tid":2014823,"uid":34470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:22:18.000Z","msg":"無變到<br />\n都係小罵大幫忙"},{"pid":"a4476ecbe85087bfb48892cfc1baba729a5b7939","tid":2014823,"uid":128261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"10b13571d4d16070272069b895d9152a9b187ae8","tid":2014823,"uid":34470,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:22:18.000Z","msg":"無變到<br />\n都係小罵大幫忙"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-13T09:23:16.000Z","msg":"有分別